description: Deletes a batch of geofences from a geofence collection.

parameters.name: CollectionName
parameters.description: The geofence collection storing the geofences to be deleted.

parameters.name: GeofenceIds
parameters.description: The batch of geofences to be deleted. (string) ---

nested_items.name: Errors
nested_items.description: Contains error details for each geofence that failed to delete.

nested_items.name: GeofenceId
nested_items.description: The geofence associated with the error message.

nested_items.name: Code
nested_items.description: The error code associated with the batch request error.

nested_items.name: Message
nested_items.description: A message with the reason for the batch request error.
